  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released Deployed\u00a0on 9/22/16 11:12 CT</p><p>This is a minor release with\u00a0a few bug fixes.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.7-Staff&quot;Status&quot;Filter\">Staff &quot;Status&quot; Filter</h3><p>The &quot;Status&quot; filter was not being applied to the &quot;unassigned&quot; group of staff members listed on the &quot;Name&quot; tab of the staff index. The &quot;Status&quot; filter will now filter the results for that group accordingly.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.7-SummaryReport\">Summary Report</h3><p>Fixed an issue with the Summary Report when performing monthly rollups spanning multiple years of data where the \u00a0&quot;February&quot;\u00a0\u00a0header\u00a0was skipped for 2016.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.7-RemovingTicketItems\">Removing Ticket Items</h3><p>When removing\u00a0inventory items on a ticket, the &quot;void&quot; status option will no longer be present for non-managers, unless the item is in the &quot;backordered&quot; status.</p>",
      "representation": "export_view",
